import React from "react";
import { Nav, NavLink, NavMenu } 
    from "./NavbarElements";
  
const Navbar = () => {
  return (
    <>

          <NavLink to="/Infernoguard" activeStyle>

            Infernoguard

          </NavLink>

          <NavLink to="/Index" activeStyle>

            PA Index
            </button>

          <NavLink to="/Capstone" activeStyle>
          <button class="button">
            Capstone

          </NavLink>

          <NavLink to="/Converter" activeStyle>

            Converter
            </button>
          </NavLink>

          <button class="button">
            Animations
            </button>

        </NavMenu>
      </Nav>
    </>
  );
};
  
export default Navbar;
